************************************************************************
.options savecurrents


Vcc vcc 0 5
Vee vee 0 -5
Vin in 0 0 ac 1.0 sin(0 10m 1k)


*High pass filter

C1 in in_plus 220n
R1 in_plus 0 1k

*Amplifier
X1 in_plus in_minus vcc vee out_1 uA741
R3 in_minus out_1 100k
R4 in_minus 0 1k

*Low pass filter
R2 out_1 out 1k
C2 out 0 220n



